N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 2430.5 - List of records

State Regulations
A current list, by subject matter, of all records of the
board available for public inspection shall be maintained by the records access
officer, which list shall be available for public inspection and
copying. Notes
